Test case 1, Authorization.

1. Open browser Chrome
2. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login. - page is opened
3. Enter "Student" to "Email" field. - "Student" is displayed in "Email" field
4. Enter "909090" to "Password" field. - "******" is displayed in "Password" field
5. Click on "Вход" button. - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/
6. Check that: user is equal "Student_378"
7. Close browser Chrome

Test case 2, Add new deal.
1. Open browser Chrome
2. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login. - page is opened
3. Enter "Student" to "Email" field. - "Student" is displayed in "Email" field
4. Enter "909090" to "Password" field. - "******" is displayed in "Password" field
5. Click on "Вход" button. - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/
6. Click on menu item "Сделки" -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
7. Click on "+" button - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal/edit.
8. Choose "Obmen" in dropdown list "Тип сделки" - "Obmen" is displayed in "Тип сделки" field
9. Choose "2Вася" in dropdown list "Покупатель" - "2Вася" is displayed in "Покупатель" field
10. Choose "test" in dropdown list "Поставщик" - "test" is displayed in "Поставщик" field
11. Click on "Создать" button -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
12. In the last bottom field: second cell is equal "Obmen".
13. Close browser Chrome

Test case 3, Edit "Тип сделки" field in a deal.
Pre-conditions: new deal is added.
1. Open browser Chrome
2. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login. - page is opened
3. Enter "Student" to "Email" field. - "Student" is displayed in "Email" field
4. Enter "909090" to "Password" field. - "******" is displayed in "Password" field
5. Click on "Вход" button. - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/
6. Click on menu item "Сделки" -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
7. Click on "+" button - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal/edit.
8. Choose "Obmen" in dropdown list "Тип сделки" - "Obmen" is displayed in "Тип сделки" field
9. Choose "2Вася" in dropdown list "Покупатель" - "2Вася" is displayed in "Покупатель" field
10. Choose "test" in dropdown list "Поставщик" - "test" is displayed in "Поставщик" field
11. Click on "Создать" button -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
12. Click on the last bottom field - page with deal is opened.
13. Choose "Бонус" in dropdown list "Тип сделки" - "Бонус" is displayed in "Тип сделки" field
14. Click "Сохранить" button -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
15. In the last bottom field: second cell is equal "Бонус".
16. Close browser Chrome

Test case 4, Deal with spare part cannot be deleted.
1. Open browser Chrome
2. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login. - page is opened
3. Enter "Student" to "Email" field. - "Student" is displayed in "Email" field
4. Enter "909090" to "Password" field. - "******" is displayed in "Password" field
5. Click on "Вход" button. - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/
6. Click on menu item "Сделки" -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
7. Click on "+" button - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal/edit.
8. Choose "Obmen" in dropdown list "Тип сделки" - "Obmen" is displayed in "Тип сделки" field
9. Choose "2Вася" in dropdown list "Покупатель" - "2Вася" is displayed in "Покупатель" field
10. Choose "test" in dropdown list "Поставщик" - "test" is displayed in "Поставщик" field
11. Click "Создать" button. -  redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal.
12. Click on the last bottom field -  page with deal is opened.
13. Click "+" button - page with spare is opened.
14. Enter "1" in "Spare count" field - "1" is displayed in "Spare count" field.
15. Choose "Obmen 01.01.2014 00:00" in the last bottom string of dropdown list "Сделка" - "Obmen 01.01.2014 00:00" is displayed in "Сделка" field.
16. Choose "lastSpare" in dropdown list "Деталь" - "lastSpare" is displayed in "Деталь" field.
17. Click on "Создать" button -> redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/spare_operation
18. Click on menu item "Сделки" -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
19. Click on the last bottom field -  page with deal is opened.
20. The last bottom string of "Список запчастей" form is exist "pastSpare" in the second cell.
21. Click "Удалить" button -> redirect to page with message "404 Страница не найдена".
22. Click on "на главную страницу" link. - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/
23. Click on menu item "Сделки".
24. Click on the last bottom field -  page with deal is opened.
25. The last bottom field of "Список запчастей" form exist in the second cell "lastSpare".
26. Close browser.

Test case 5, Add spare part with invalid value to deal (negative test).
1. Open browser Chrome
2. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login. - page is opened
3. Enter "Student" to "Email" field. - "Student" is displayed in "Email" field
4. Enter "909090" to "Password" field. - "******" is displayed in "Password" field
5. Click on "Вход" button. - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/
6. Click on menu item "Сделки" -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
7. Click on "+" button - redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal/edit.
8. Choose "Obmen" in dropdown list "Тип сделки" - "Obmen" is displayed in "Тип сделки" field
9. Choose "2Вася" in dropdown list "Покупатель" - "2Вася" is displayed in "Покупатель" field
10. Choose "test" in dropdown list "Поставщик" - "test" is displayed in "Поставщик" field
11. Click "+" button. -  redirect to page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal/edit.
12. Click on menu item "Сделки" -> page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal is opened.
13. Click on the last bottom field -  page with deal is opened.
14. Click "+" button - page with spare is opened.
15. Enter "*" in "Spare count" field - "*" is displayed in "Spare count" field.
16. Choose "Obmen 01.01.2014 00:00" in the last bottom string of dropdown list "Сделка" - "Obmen 01.01.2014 00:00" is displayed in "Сделка" field.
17. Choose "lastSpare" in dropdown list "Деталь" - "lastSpare" is displayed in "Деталь" field.
18. Click on "Создать" button -> "Spare count" field is highlighted in red and error message is displayed.
19. Close browser.
